friendLines.title: Hello
friendLines.description: *Yawn* That was a refreshing sleep. Ah, Traveler, we meet again! What? You don't remember me? Ahaha, well, allow me to join you on your quest once again. I must see to it that the bards of the world tell the Traveler's tales!

friendLines.title: Chat: Playing the Lyre
friendLines.description: Sure, I'll play you another tune, but it'll cost you an apple.

friendLines.title: Chat: Apple Cider
friendLines.description: Right now I wish I was sitting at the top of a tree, looking out over a meadow, cider in hand...

friendLines.title: Chat: Ballads
friendLines.description: Come on Traveler, let's go! The world is full of lost ballads just waiting to be rediscovered.

friendLines.title: When It Rains
friendLines.description: Let's go jumping in puddles and see who can make the biggest splash!

friendLines.title: After the Rain
friendLines.description: It's stopped raining already? A shame, I wanted to play some more.

friendLines.title: When It Snows
friendLines.description: Let's wait till the snow gets heavier and have a snowball fight!

friendLines.title: When the Wind Is Blowing
friendLines.description: The wind has returned! Quick, let's go gliding!

friendLines.title: Good Morning
friendLines.description: Morning! Ah... what's in store for today?

friendLines.title: Good Afternoon
friendLines.description: My tummy is rumbling, but I can't get caught pilfering food from the Dawn Winery again... Oh, it's you! Where are you heading? May I join?

friendLines.title: Good Evening
friendLines.description: Hmm, I'm still not sleepy. Fancy an evening stroll?

friendLines.title: Good Night
friendLines.description: Off to the land of nod? Haha, farewell, my friend!

friendLines.title: About Venti
friendLines.description: Practice? Me? There's no need — I already know every song in Teyvat!

friendLines.title: About Us: New Songs
friendLines.description: I have decided to write a song about you! What are you giving me that look for? Can't afford it? Don't be preposterous, the price for you, my friend, is precisely zero Mora! Although... one thing you could do is tell me a few more of your stories!

friendLines.title: About Us: Heroes
friendLines.description: Haha, once the {M#hero}{F#heroine} in the song has actually rescued the {M#princess}{F#prince}, I will ensure this song spreads to every corner of the continent!

friendLines.title: About Us: Apostles
friendLines.description: Ahh... an evening breeze really sets the mood for becoming my disciple, don't you think? We can do it right now... you just need to make me a small offering...

unlockConditions.unlockText: Complete "Song of the Dragon and Freedom"

friendLines.title: About Us: Requests
friendLines.description: What's that? You think I should try harder to be a good Anemo Archon? Well, you could be a better devotee too... you could be more pious, more passionate, or... um...

unlockConditions.unlockText: Complete "Song of the Dragon and Freedom"

friendLines.title: About the Vision
friendLines.description: Hmm? You want to know about my Vision? Oh, go on then, take a look for yourself. I can make you a matching one if you like! Hehehe.

friendLines.title: Something to Share
friendLines.description: Olah! Haha, that's how the Hilichurls say "hello." Why, I learned it to aid with my songwriting, of course! Vast knowledge makes for a richer composition... That said, I haven't actually written any songs in Hilichurlian so far...

friendLines.title: Interesting Things
friendLines.description: Traveler, have you ever seen a Cecilia? It's a magnificent white wildflower that only grows on the most remote mountains and clifftops. To me, at least, it is the most beautiful flower in all of Teyvat.

friendLines.title: About Jean
friendLines.description: Acting Grand Master Jean... Well, what do you think of her? Yes, I couldn't agree more: conscientious, courageous... kind and considerate too. Reminds me of another good friend...

friendLines.title: About Diluc
friendLines.description: I'm not surprised you want to befriend Master Diluc. Just think of all the vintage wine he must have stored away... Mwuhahaha... Huh? He doesn't let you sample it? Not even the slightest drop? Huh... Well, I guess you can still appreciate the aroma. That's still better than no wine at all, right? No?

friendLines.title: About Barbara
friendLines.description: The darling Deaconess with the sweet singing voice — do you know her? You do? Idol, huh? Meet and greets? Concerts? Wow... That's the power of music for you...

friendLines.title: About Razor
friendLines.description: Ah yes, the white-haired fellow from Wolvendom? Raised by wolves? Really? ... No wonder his scent is so familiar...

friendLines.title: About Mona
friendLines.description: Oh, that astrologer? How should I put it? Fortune-telling and my singing are the same: Both lead to you being so poor you can't even cough up the money for a drink! ...You think that astrology is a cultural tradition, so at least still has some value? Hmph, so rude. In that case, so too is singing, so it still has its value too!

friendLines.title: About Diona
friendLines.description: There's a special drink known far and wide at Cat's Tail. But it ah... ahh... ACHOO! *sniffs* How about you go and fetch one for me? I'll be truly thankful, I promise.

friendLines.title: About Albedo
friendLines.description: How do you explain white chalk in black soil, or the earth's dense crust amidst the emptiness of space? Same reason the purest soil gave birth to human life... It's an ancient power with unmistakable properties. Trying to harness it is dangerous indeed, I can't imagine what would happen if someone lost control of it in the city... Ah, never mind! What goes on within Mondstadt's walls is up to Mondstadt's people to deal with!

friendLines.title: About Morax
friendLines.description: Have you seen that gentleman around? Huh? He's just a normal man by the name of Zhongli now? That must be quite the change for that old block-head. Come with me to see him, will you? I have a vintage I dug up from Windrise that I can take as a condolence gift. Oh, ahh... did he still seem strong when you saw him? How strong? Am I likely to get blown away?

friendLines.title: About Eula
friendLines.description: Eula has good taste when it comes to beverages of the alcoholic variety. Come summer or winter, she always likes them ice-cold. That's rare among Mondstadters these days! She and I would make great drinking buddies. Huh? My songs about the Lawrence Clan... She's heard them already? Eh, no harm done. Maybe she and I can do a duet sometime!

friendLines.title: About Baal
friendLines.description: So, I hear you defeated the mighty Raiden Shogun? Ah, I recall the days when she was a kagemusha, seeking to perfect her martial prowess. Hehe, she now no doubt employs a wide range of reasoning to get you to train with her. Oh but yes, come close and I shall let you in on her weakness — desserts!

friendLines.title: About Buer
friendLines.description: The first thing you think of when you hear "Dendro Archon" is her power over dreams. Her dreams are akin to my ballads: full of emotion and imagination. It goes without saying that we get along really well.

unlockConditions.unlockText: Complete "Akasha Pulses, the Kalpa Flame Rises"

friendLines.title: About Furina
friendLines.description: A bard must be versed in both music and song, but a stage performer requires far more skills than just these... Hey, don't you think we should invite her over to put on a show at the next Windblume Festival? ...Huh? You want me to talk about how she saved Fontaine? Well, I mean, she's such a talented artiste, it's no wonder. I wouldn't be surprised even if she'd saved the entire world.

friendLines.title: About Haborym
friendLines.description: This world sure is cruel, forcing generation upon generation of human heroes to become cannon fodder in the fight against darkness. But, under Mavuika's leadership, they achieved a truly god-like feat... Hehe, starting with "her," I suppose the Natlanese have always been like that. Ah, right! I heard Mavuika likes to drink! Are you thinking what I'm thinking...?

friendLines.title: More About Venti: I
friendLines.description: Perfect timing, Traveler! I was about to ask you — what is your greatest wish?

friendLines.title: More About Venti: II
friendLines.description: There's never a dull moment traveling with you! The only minor inconvenience is that pesky little pixie thing that follows you everywhere... She never stops eating — I can't begin to imagine how much you spend on food!

friendLines.title: More About Venti: III
friendLines.description: The Pyro Archon is a wayward, warmongering wretch, and the Geo Archon is a brutish, blundering buffoon! How do I know? Because, this is written in the epic poems of days gone by!

friendLines.title: More About Venti: IV
friendLines.description: Celestia... I'm not sure even I could fly that far. In any case, the water there tastes foul, and the fruit is bland. You know what that means? No cider! Haha, in that case, I wouldn't go there even if I was invited.

friendLines.title: More About Venti: V
friendLines.description: My greatest wish? It has always been to roam free and experience the whole world. Now, I would add that wherever I go, it simply must be with you! Each day with you is an adventure, and where adventurers go, storytellers must follow!

friendLines.title: Venti's Hobbies
friendLines.description: I like to drink! And I like the wind! If only there were such a thing as wind-brewed cider...

friendLines.title: Venti's Troubles
friendLines.description: I'm actually highly allergic to cats. I start sneezing as soon as they enter the vicinity, and... Aah... Aa-choo! Ugh, apparently I can't even THINK about cats without sneezing. Do you think there is a cure for this monstrous affliction?

friendLines.title: Favorite Food
friendLines.description: Here, have an apple. I just picked it. Look how ripe and juicy it is... *munching* ... Truly the fruit of the gods.

friendLines.title: Least Favorite Food
friendLines.description: Hmm, what's that tasty morsel you've got there...? Eww! A melted cheese pancake? A smelly, sticky, slimy, disgusting mess!

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: I
friendLines.description: Ahh, quite delightful! So... could I get the same again tomorrow? ...And maybe the day after that?

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: II
friendLines.description: Oof, I'm so full... I'll have to pass on the post-meal fruits this time...

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: III
friendLines.description: I can't believe it, but I don't think I can stomach this... Oh boy... What a predicament.

friendLines.title: Birthday
friendLines.description: Someone once told me you're supposed to eat a cake on your birthday... Tada! Here's your birthday cake — it's apple-flavored! And here's a spoon. The cake didn't rise properly in the oven... That's why it looks more akin to an apple pie... Ugh, baking is really quite complicated!

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Intro
friendLines.description: Woah! What was that?

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Building Up
friendLines.description: Good work. Shall we repose for a moment with a tune? Shall it be a capriccio or a serenade?

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Climax
friendLines.description: Come, sit with me. I've written a new poem. I call it "Wind of the Traveler."

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Conclusion
friendLines.description: Hmm... Though I've long since viewed this scenery a great many times, there is something different about seeing it again with you. Surely you're not still concealing some other wondrous abilities? Hmm, even if you were, it would simply further prove that my intuition is correct.

actionLines.title: Opening Treasure Chest: I
actionLines.description: *clears throat* Have you heard The Ballad of the Treasure Chest?

actionLines.title: Opening Treasure Chest: III
actionLines.description: What a find! I wonder how many bottles this'll be worth...

actionLines.title: Low HP: I
actionLines.description: Ugh, I'm not in the mood for this!

actionLines.title: Fallen: II
actionLines.description: Oh no, my lyre is broken...

actionLines.title: Joining Party: I
actionLines.description: Give me a moment to compose myself.

actionLines.title: Joining Party: II
actionLines.description: Didn't keep you waiting, did I?
